    <p>
      Quebec Studies              : A multidisciplinary course that looks at Quebec with an aim of integrating key social, economic, cultural, political and historical aspects.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Sonia Cancian (Fall)                  </p>

    
