      Instructors:                        Morton Weinfeld (Winter)                  </p>

    
          <ul class="catalog-notes">
              <li>Restrictions: Open to students following the Minor Concentration in Canadian Ethnic Studies; or to students with at least nine credits, three at the 300 level, in the social sciences; or with permission of instructor. Not open to students who took CANS 404 in 2007-08.</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

  </div> <!-- /.node -->
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
                </ul>
      
      
            </div>

    
  
